ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n有，依家本土片要用粗口博人笑，一係就踩大陸人大家就笑得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7272ee16773f3ded8f3f011afdac5597a0ff51bf","tid":114597,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"真係搵唔到有人可以同星爺比較<br />\n星爺既電影，就算你之前睇過100次，知道晒啲笑位係邊度，但你仲會笑<br />\n呢個就係佢嘅魅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ff8019ab45bf70495a3c34ed374c4ecab2ea83","tid":114597,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個人覺得梁朝偉搞笑唔差得過星爺，<br />\n只係佢唔鐘意被定位做只識搞笑嘅藝人.</blockquote><br />\n東京攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n韓城攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n街運超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東成西就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d81e545f73d9c912bba0c9bbe3cec8be972a851","tid":114597,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>許冠文算唔算?</blockquote><br />\n電影台睇過半斤八兩 完全唔知有咩好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雞同鴨講幾好笑"},{"pid":"597b4fd2c3ad6af763d49f9c64424d66ed3ca72f","tid":114597,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:31:13.000Z","msg":"達哥"},{"pid":"e0e63f0da45ae54928c3e7145634c8385a8ece5f","tid":114597,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T08:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>許冠文算唔算?</bloc